==Character==

===Appearance===
* Shikinami wears a serafuku with short sleeves and a brown collar, shared with [[Ayanami]].
* She has brown hair in a small ponytail secured by a black bow and has brown eyes.

=== Personality ===
* Shikinami has a somewhat tsundere-like personality, and does speak in a fairly monotonous tone. She acts as a foil to Ayanami.

==Trivia==
*Sunk by USS [http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/USS_Growler_%28SS-215%29 Growler], 12 September 1944 in the [http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/South_China_Sea South China Sea] ([http://toolserver.org/~geohack/geohack.php?pagename=Japanese_destroyer_Shikinami&params=18_16_N_114_40_E_type:landmark_region:XZ_region:#regional 18°16′N 114°40′E])
